.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, police-officer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, romance
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, gospel
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the manager##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Sport          | volleyball        | soccer |
| Job           | police-officer | manager    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance        | adventure  |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | techno       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

